imageDescription: A dog being a dog: Amos
name: Amos
story: My name is AMOS (SRC#1945) and I am a un-neutered, male Standard Schnauzer . I was born in November, 2017  and I weigh approximately 25 - 28 pounds. I am micro-chipped, have all required vaccinations, have not yet been neutered and cannot be neutered until I am a minimum of one year old because of my growth plates. My breeder has me health tested.

name: Achilles
story: Achilles is a 4 year old male chocolate Plott Hound mix. Achilles was treated by HSDC for heartworms. Achilles is friendly and playful.

name: Blaze
story: Blaze is a 4 year old Jack Russell Terrier. Blaze is sweet and playful. He LOVES tennis balls. He would do well in a home with older children or no children.

name: Gordo
story: Gordo is a 4 - 5 yr. old, 8 lb., Chihuahua mix looking for his forever home. He is a somewhat shy little guy who was picked up as a stray. He is not leash trained but with time he should be fine. He just needs someone who is willing to work with a shy dog and give him confidence. He likes other small dogs but avoids large dogs, and he is fine with cats. He is partially housebroke and will use a dog door.

name: Cyrus
story: These sweet babes, along with their mom Carmandy, came to us from an Arkansas family who could not care for them. They are a spunk, people-loving bunch who are eager for attention. They can't wait to find a family who enjoys games in the yard and long walks. Please help these little cuties find the forever families they deserve!

name: Coco
story: Coco hasn't had the best life bougth by someone to breed him then had to live in a horse stall most of his life he has been in a real home for about 6 months but since he was not socialized he's fearful specially around new environments and loud crazy kids

name: Tiger
story: Tiger has been in the shelter almost 12 weeks! He is very sad at the shelter and needs a foster placement or a forever home. Please keep sharing his post. Tiger is a three year old male Boxer mix. He loves to go on long walks.

name: Echo
story: Echo is a one year old male Hound & Mountain Cur mix. Echo is energetic and friendly. He loves to go on walks.

name: Camille
story: These sweet babes, along with their mom Carmandy, came to us from an Arkansas family who could not care for them. They are a spunk, people-loving bunch who are eager for attention. They can't wait to find a family who enjoys games in the yard and long walks. Please help these little cuties find the forever families they deserve!

name: Obie
story: Obie is a one year old male Dalmatian and Lab mix. Obie is friendly and outgoing. He loves to play. Obie is friendly with other dogs, cats, and children.
